Package: retrosheetshow
Title: Access and Parse Retrosheet Baseball Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Travis", "Gerke", , "tgerke@mail.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a convenient and tidy interface for accessing Retrosheet 
    baseball data, including play-by-play event files, box scores, and other 
    historical baseball data. Functions follow tidyverse principles for easy 
    integration into data analysis workflows.
URL: https://tgerke.github.io/retrosheetshow/, https://github.com/tgerke/retrosheetshow
BugReports: https://github.com/tgerke/retrosheetshow/issues
